basics.name: Cameron Wilby
basics.label: Software Engineer
basics.summary: Software Engineer with experience building Web/Mobile applications, DevOps, Service Integration and Project Management.

highlights: Design West Engineering - https://designwesteng.com - Updated a Microsoft Access application to an ASP.NET/KnockoutJS web application with project management, SSRS reporting, and payroll functionality.

QDRO Division - https://qdrodivision.com - Developed a Laravel/Vue application to help QDRO attorneys manage their cases, share case statuses with clients, and generate documents from pre-built templates.
Rowland Water District - https://www.rowlandwater.com/ - Developed an ASP.NET/KnockoutJS web application for an on-site payment kiosk at Rowland Water District.
PMD Alliance - https://www.pmdalliance.org/ - Developed a Laravel/React Native application to help people with Parkinsons find nearby exercise and support groups.
GSI - https://gsi.loci.ca/ - Developed an educational game with Laravel/Angular to create awareness around the length of time COVID-19 can survive on various surfaces.

work.summary: Full stack development/maintenance for an automated email marketing platform.
highlights: Developed and maintained third party integration with Stripe, Shopify, and ClickFunnels.
Built a continuous integration/testing workflow to increase code quality.
Worked with customer success team to identify new features and triage bug fixes.

work.summary: Created a 12 week development curriculum and learning environment.
highlights: Built curriculum and presented daily live-coding sessions to classes of 16 students.
Sourced real-world projects from local businesses as final projects for students.
Learned presentation and how to run a lean startup.

work.summary: Full stack development/maintenance for a US-based bankruptcy case management system.
highlights: Built a portal for users to invite debtor attorneys to upload documents for a case.
Designed and implemented a system to automate case auditing.
Learned .NET best practices and advanced web development techniques.
Fully remote team using Skype and screen sharing to facilitate standups and code review.

volunteer.summary: Gave talks about JavaScript and techniques for building web applications
highlights: Founded a fundamental JS meetup with coding exercises and focus on core Javascript fundamentals
